References: <noah-130493102106@noah.apple.com> <1qhib6$ghh@pandora.sdsu.edu> <C5HyIz.8At@cs.dal.ca> <1993Apr15.004107.12539@leland.Stanford.EDU> <C5Iz7n.Kyv@cs.dal.ca>
