Subject: HELP - SCSI Woes on Mac IIfx
Keywords: SCSI, IIfx
Sender: lumpkin@amelia.nas.nasa.gov (Forrest E. Lumpkin III)
Organization: NASA Ames Research Center 
Date: Fri, 16 Apr 93 23:31:41 GMT
Message-ID: <1993Apr16.233141.16769@nas.nasa.gov>
