From: ray@netcom.com (Ray Fischer)
Subject: Re: 68040 Specs.
Message-ID: <rayC5Myqo.o8@netcom.com>
Organization: Netcom. San Jose, California
References: <1qkr6n$18c@bigboote.WPI.EDU>
