Subject: Re: Why does Apple give us a confusing message?
Message-ID: <1qs4fjINN74f@shelley.u.washington.edu>
Date: 18 Apr 93 17:51:47 GMT
Article-I.D.: shelley.1qs4fjINN74f
References: <C5nGII.BGx@news2.cis.umn.edu>
