Subject: Stereo sound problem (?) on mac games
Date: 18 Apr 1993 20:56:52 GMT
Organization: UC San Diego Chemistry
Lines: 62
Distribution: world
Message-ID: <1qsfak$skc@network.ucsd.edu>
